{"tid":735014,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我迫不及待好想玩玩了","createTime":"2018-07-09T06:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T06:52:47.000Z","uid":60150,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f6e1750c0239198642911c987bdf51784b67cb","tid":735014,"uid":60150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:50:26.000Z","msg":"就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會首先經香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡直是公司權力核心。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715b755936f59be38e6887b57585065a989c1046","tid":735014,"uid":168930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"541b56fa7515b85453df7cc4e4aee5d52255474b","tid":735014,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r